---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Use Cases | BeaconGuard Assurance">
  <section>
    <h1>Use Cases</h1>
    <p>
      BeaconGuard supports governed AI programs where financial workflow decisions must remain
      deterministic, auditable, and operationally safe.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>High-trust Use Cases</h2>
    <div class="section-grid">
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Regulated workflow control</h3>
        <p>Decision gates for AI-assisted actions in controlled environments with review requirements.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Customer operational controls</h3>
        <p>Governed AI-mediated financial interactions where authorization mistakes can create operational and control risk.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Partner ecosystem integrations</h3>
        <p>Cross-team integrations with deterministic policy identity, bounded trust, and shared evidence expectations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Operational Patterns</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Front-office assistants requiring policy gating.</li>
      <li>Internal decision support systems with strict approval rules.</li>
      <li>Cross-service orchestration with central policy control and bounded trust boundaries.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Sector Coverage</h2>
    <p>
      BeaconGuard is not limited to one industry.
      It is intended for financial and enterprise environments where AI decisions must follow
      explicit governance controls and support evidence-driven review.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Explore by outcome</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/platform">Understand platform coverage</a></li>
      <li><a href="/trust-assurance">Review assurance model</a></li>
      <li><a href="/deployment">Compare deployment posture</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="page-actions">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="/design-partner-program">Request governance review support</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="/contact">Start a platform discussion</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
